title: Ep. 19 - All streamers are depressed
description: Hey, paisanos! In this weeks episode of The Yard, the boys are up to no good once again. QT runs face first into a glass door, Ludwig recounts how every streamer has depression, and a fan of the podcast pulls off a wild public stunt.
